<br>
You have a point about people needing to see what we do.  They also need to see us doing it all the time--thus the need for something to eliminate excessive downtime due to mana needs. Do this, and nothing else for wizards might be needed, as we could nuke to our potential in every fight, and be ready for the next in a timely fashion.  This is part of why no one ever 'did' dungeons like they envisioned... 2 or 3 fights and you have to sit for about 10 minutes, which is just about when the respawn hits.  <br>
<br>
